This directory contains the various settings files for the xorg-gui program.

alias.txt
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file should contain the strings from drivers.txt, followed by a colon ":"
and the template name to use. For example, nvidia-100.14.11 will use the 
"nvidia" template drivers. 

definition.txt
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file lists the dpi resolutions available in the GUI tool

depth.txt
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file lists the available color depths we allow in the GUI

drivers.txt
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file provides a list of driver names which will show up in the "Advanced"
tab of the GUI. This driver should correspond to a line in the alias.txt file

refresh.txt
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file contains a list of valid refresh rates for the GUI tool.

resolutions.txt
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file contains the list of resolutions the user may select in the GUI.
